sentences.sentence: Together, the family entered the little unpainted farmhouse.
sentences.translation: 全家人一起走进了尚未油漆的农舍。

sentences.sentence: The section that was painted was so small, and the unpainted section was so big!
sentences.translation: 这是画的部分是如此之小，和粉刷一节是如此之大！

sentences.sentence: That unpainted car would be the beginning of an auto company thinking open-source.
sentences.translation: 生产未经上漆的汽车只是汽车厂商开源生产的开始。
